creator: Kuailian App OÜ
descriptionHtml:
Create your wallet on the Ehtereum mainchain, and connect it with the ZkSync sidechain in order to receive Kuailian rewards on a daily basis.

Some of the perks that we offer to our users are:

- Secured wallet which is under full control of the user. You can store, send, or receive securely your crypto funds. Private keys will be stored only on your phone. We will never have access to your assets.

- Receive daily payments on your Kuailian Wallet APP. Create your wallet address and connect it with the sidechain via your existing profile, and you will start receiving payments on the ZkSync wallet address.

- Withdraw to mainchain wallet. You can accumulate your funds and decide when you wish to move them to your ETH wallet on the mainchain.
descriptionShort: Receive your Kuailian rewards and bonuses easily

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Changed name of app under the icon
- Fixed bug when the app was crashing after adding more wallets
- Added more colors for different wallets
- Increased maximum number of wallets that can be added
- Implemented BIP39 standard for mnemonic passphrases
- Improved app speed when updating the balance
- Added new design of loading spinner

title: Kuailian Wallet App

creator: Kuailian App OÜ
descriptionHtml:
Create your Kuailian wallet easily and without any charge
Use the advantages of our multi-coin support, with ETH, TRX, and USDT (TRC-20).

Some of the perks we are offering to our users are:

- Private & Secured multi-wallet which is under full control of a user. You can store, send or receive your crypto assets. You will be the only owner of your private keys, even we don’t have access to them.
- Freezing your TRX and sending transactions with 0 fees.
- Receiving daily payments on your Kuailian wallet APP in USDT (TRC-20)
